TRN: Add the TRN for trainees you want to recommend. Can be empty if Provider trainee ID is provided
Provider trainee ID:
Add your trainee ID for trainees you want to recommend.

Can be empty if TRN is provided
Date standards met:
Add the date when the trainee met QTS or EYTS standards.
Must be written DD/MM/YYYY. 
For example, if the trainee met the teaching standard on 20 July 2022, write '20/07/2022'.
The date must be in the past.
If the trainee has not met the QTS or EYTS, leave the cell empty.
